**MACRO/MARKETS:** Google's AI-powered conversational search on YouTube signals accelerating shift in digital advertising monetization models; threatens traditional search-based ad inventory while creating new engagement metrics that could reshape ad-tech valuations across Big Tech and programmatic platforms.

**AI/ML:** Real-time multimodal conversational AI (Gemini Omni) embedded in consumer platforms validates enterprise demand for conversational interfaces; banking analytics teams should monitor latency/cost implications for deploying similar conversational ECL model explainability or real-time credit risk dashboards.

**BUILDER:** Gemini Omni integration demonstrates viability of low-latency streaming video + LLM architecture;
